snippet.title: Chainitaire
snippet.description:
Chainitaire is a solitare type game I made for #mizjam1 where the theme was that everyone was using the same art kit.

Play online or download at:
https://anttihaavikko.itch.io/chainitaire

Jam site:
https://itch.io/jam/miz-jam-1

Used art kit:
https://kenney.nl/assets/bit-pack
